{
  "ProofStructure": [
    {
      "proposition": [
        "The smallest Norwegian number is 1344"
      ],
      "type": "Show"
    },
    {
      "meaning": [
        "A number is called Norwegian if it has three distinct positive divisors whose sum is equal to 2022."
      ],
      "symbol": "Norwegian number",
      "type": "Define"
    },
    {
      "comment": "The total number of positive divisors of a Norwegian number is allowed to be larger than 3.",
      "type": "Hint"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "1344 is a Norwegian number"
      ],
      "reasons": [
        "6, 672 and 1344 are three distinct divisors of 1344",
        "6+672+1344=2022"
      ],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "comment": "It remains to show that this is the smallest such number.",
      "type": "Hint"
    },
    {
      "assumption": [
        "Assume for contradiction that N<1344 is Norwegian"
      ],
      "type": "Assume"
    },
    {
      "condition": [
        "N/a, N/b and N/c be the three distinct divisors of N",
        "a<b<c"
      ],
      "type": "Fix",
      "var_list": [
        "a",
        "b",
        "c"
      ]
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "2022=N\\left(\\frac1a+\\frac1b+\\frac1c\\right)<1344\\left(\\frac1a+\\frac1b+\\frac1c\\right)"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "\\left(\\frac1a+\\frac1b+\\frac1c\\right)>\\frac{2022}{1344}=\\frac{337}{224}=\\frac32+\\frac1{224}"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "assumption": [
        "a>1"
      ],
      "type": "Assume"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "\\frac{1}{a}+\\frac{1}{b}+\\frac{1}{c}\\leqslant\\frac{1}{2}+\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{1}{4}=\\frac{13}{12}<\\frac{3}{2}"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "a=1"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "b<4"
      ],
      "reasons": [
        "otherwise 1+\\dfrac{1}{b}+\\dfrac{1}{c}\\leqslant1+\\dfrac{1}{4}+\\dfrac{1}{5}<\\dfrac{3}{2}"
      ],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "comment": "This leaves two cases to check, b=2 and b=3.",
      "type": "Hint"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Case b=3.",
      "type": "Hint"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "\\frac1c>\\frac32+\\frac1{224}-1-\\frac13>\\frac16"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "c=4 or c=5"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "assumption": [
        "c=4"
      ],
      "type": "Assume"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "2022=N\\left(1+\\dfrac13+\\dfrac14\\right)=\\dfrac{19}{12}N"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "This is impossible as 19 \\nmid 2022"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "assumption": [
        "c=5"
      ],
      "type": "Assume"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "2022=N\\left(1+\\frac13+\\frac15\\right)=\\frac{23}{15}N"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "This is impossible, as 23 \\nmid 2022"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Case b=2.",
      "type": "Hint"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "c<224"
      ],
      "reasons": [
        "\\frac1c>\\frac32+\\frac1{224}-1-\\frac12=\\frac1{224}"
      ],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "2022=N\\left(1+\\frac12+\\frac1c\\right)=\\frac{3c+2}{2c}N\\Rightarrow(3c+2)N=4044c"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "Since (c,3c-2)=(c,2)\\in\\{1,2\\}, then 3c+2\\mid8088=2^3\\cdot3\\cdot337 which implies that 3c+2\\mid2^3\\cdot337"
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    },
    {
      "proposition": [
        "But since 3c+2\\geqslant3\\cdot3+2>8=2^3 and 3c+2\\neq337, then it must hold that 3c+2\\geqslant2\\cdot337, contradicting c<224."
      ],
      "reasons": [],
      "type": "Have"
    }
  ]
}